WgygAE9XQ&oe=671A4E2A"}, "display_name": "VR Club", "keywords": [], "long_description": "24/7 VR music festival, hang out with friends and other music lovers from around the world in sound-reactive spaces. Experience amazing light shows and fireworks like never before! Find yourself on the tropical island during sunset with beautiful event decorations and two music scenes, one is on the pier just above the water, and the second is in caves under erupting Volcano. Dive into the world of wonders, and enjoy your stay. Complete daily quests to earn rewards, customize your avatar, and uniquely identify yourself at the next-generation concert. Innovative solutions like dynamic playlists, hand tracking, 120Hz, haptic feedback, full-body avatar, and VJ spot - allow you to create a visual spectacle for others and immerse yourself in music. All these elements are synchronized with everyone in the club! To have more fun there are dance games and activities, for example: \u201cNever have I ever...\" After all the craziness you can ease your mind in the beautiful rest area.", "short_description": "24/7 VR music festival, hang out with friends and other music lovers from around the world in sound-reactive spaces. Experience amazing light shows and fireworks like never before! Find yourself on the tropical island during sunset with beautiful event decorations and two music scenes. Dive into the world of wonders, and enjoy your stay."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrclub.live/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "XRCOO", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://vrclub.live/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "668538087410124"}, {"id": "548013192910304"}, {"id": "361620458439488"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": 